sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Blazor as Blazor Client
    participant API as TranslationController
    participant Service as TranslationService
    participant Telemetry as CustomTelemetryService
    participant Logger as Serilog
    participant OpenAI as Azure OpenAI
    participant AppIns as Application Insights
    
    User->>Blazor: Enter text "Hello"
    User->>Blazor: Click Translate
    
    Blazor->>API: POST /api/translation/translate<br/>{text: "Hello"}
    
    Note over API: Validate Request
    API->>Logger: Log translation request
    Logger->>AppIns: Send structured log
    
    API->>Service: TranslateAsync(request)
    
    Note over Service: Start stopwatch
    Service->>Logger: Log translation attempt
    
    Service->>OpenAI: CreateChatCompletionsAsync()<br/>System: Victorian English<br/>User: "Hello"
    
    Note over OpenAI: GPT-4 Processing
    OpenAI-->>Service: "Good day to you, kind sir"
    
    Note over Service: Stop stopwatch (1250ms)
    Service->>Telemetry: TrackTranslationRequest()<br/>{InputLength: 5, OutputLength: 27,<br/>Success: true, ProcessingTimeMs: 1250}
    
    Telemetry->>AppIns: Track custom event
    
    Service->>Logger: Log translation success
    Logger->>AppIns: Send structured log
    
    Service-->>API: TranslationResponse<br/>{originalText, translatedText,<br/>timestamp, processingTimeMs}
    
    API->>Logger: Log successful response
    Logger->>AppIns: Send structured log
    
    API-->>Blazor: 200 OK<br/>Translation response JSON
    
    Blazor->>Blazor: Update UI with translation
    Blazor->>User: Display "Good day to you, kind sir"
    
    Note over AppIns: Metrics aggregated<br/>for dashboards
